Class PersonalityInsights

public class PersonalityInsights
extends WatsonService

The Watson Personality Insights service uses linguistic analytics to extract a spectrum of cognitive and social characteristics from the text data that a person generates through blogs, tweets, forum posts, and more.

v2

Method Detail

getProfile

public Profile getProfile(Map<String,Object> params)
Accepts text or a Content object and responds with a Profile with a tree of characteristics that include personality, needs, and values. If you include either created or updated timestamps, the response also includes a summary of the author's writing habits with respect to time of day.

Parameters:
params - The parameters to generate the profile. Either text or content need to be specified
Returns:
The personality profile
